display_long_description:
Welcome to Tempo Travelers - where you need to keep moving, ok, please?
 
ALPHA GAMEPLAY
Compete with up to 4 players on obby tracks
Bump other Tempos into the void
Collect coins for high score
Master drifts and timed jumps to stay ahead
Chase down the crown in a wild tag mini-game
 
COMING NEXT >>
 
RHYTHM SOLO
Perfect your timing as you guide your Tempo through stunning single-player worlds! Each level pulses with original music, creating an unforgettable journey through visually spectacular environments.
 
YOUR TEMPO, YOUR STYLE
Start with your own Tempo and make it uniquely yours. Earn rewards through gameplay to unlock customization options in a fresh Mixed Reality Gift Shop.
 
WORLD ART
Some of the most mind-blowing VR environments are being handcrafted for you. Get a sneak peek on our discord, today!
 
LAUNCH TOGETHER
Tempo Travelers is slowly rolling out! As an alpha player, you'll get:
• First access to new worlds and game modes
• Free gameplay during testing
• A voice in shaping the game's future
• Access to special community events and challenges
 
Join our Discord community to connect with other players, share feedback, and help make Tempo Travelers even more chaotic.
 
Free to download and play - grab your headset and move.ok.please!
